PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a CONVENTION for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION with respect to taxes on income and on capital between Canada and the Republic of TRINIDAD AND TOBAGO, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing either the Hon. Roy MacLaren, Kathryn E. McCallion, or High Commissioner Marc Lemieux, to sign it instead.

precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a CONVENTION for
the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION with
respect to taxes on income and on capital between Canada and the Republic
of TRINIDAD AND TOBAGO, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers
authorizing either the Hon. Roy MacLaren, Kathryn E. McCallion, or High
Commissioner Marc Lemieux, to sign it instead.
